        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;IRS Customer Service Improvement Act&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;This bill prohibits the use of official time for specified union activities by employees of the Internal Revenue Service during the periods each year (1) beginning on February 12 and ending on May 5, and (2) beginning on September 1 and ending on November 1.&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
